#: resources/xnec2c.glade:10972
msgid ""
"Power transfer n^γ relative to this frequency step's peak.\n"
"γ = 0.5 expands weak regions, γ = 1 is linear amplitude, γ = 2 shows the "
"squared magnitude: |I|² is proportional to per-segment dissipated power (and "
"its radiated-power contribution via radiation resistance), |q|² to stored "
"electrostatic energy.\n"
"Adjust γ in the animate dialog."
msgstr ""
"Effektöverföring n^γ relativt detta frekvensstegs toppvärde.\n"
"γ = 0.5 expanderar svaga områden, γ = 1 är linjär amplitud, γ = 2 visar den "
"kvadrerade magnituden: |I|² är proportionell mot avgiven effekt per segment "
"(och dess bidrag till utstrålad effekt via strålningsresistansen), |q|² mot "
"lagrad elektrostatisk energi.\n"
"Justera γ i animeringsdialogen."

#: resources/xnec2c.glade:10973
msgid "_Power"
msgstr "_Effekt"

#: resources/xnec2c.glade:10984
msgid ""
"Logarithmic scale over a user-set range R below the peak.\n"
"Reveals weak detail that linear display hides; adjust R in the animate "
"dialog."
msgstr ""
"Logaritmisk skala över ett användarinställt omfång R under toppvärdet.\n"
"Avslöjar svaga detaljer som linjär visning döljer; justera R i "
"animeringsdialogen."

#: resources/xnec2c.glade:10985
msgid "_dB"
msgstr "_dB"

#: resources/xnec2c.glade:10996
msgid ""
"Inverse hyperbolic sine transfer: linear below the softening knee k, "
"logarithmic above.\n"
"Adjust k in the animate dialog."
msgstr ""
"Invers hyperbolisk sinusöverföring: linjär under mjukningsknät k, "
"logaritmisk däröver.\n"
"Justera k i animeringsdialogen."

#: resources/xnec2c.glade:10997
msgid "_Asinh"
msgstr "_Asinh"

#: resources/xnec2c.glade:11008
msgid ""
"μ-law companding transfer: lifts weak detail with bounded compression.\n"
"Adjust the compression in the animate dialog."
msgstr ""
"μ-law-kompanderingsöverföring: lyfter fram svaga detaljer med begränsad "
"kompression.\n"
"Justera kompressionen i animeringsdialogen."

#: resources/xnec2c.glade:11009
msgid "μ-_law"
msgstr "μ-_law"

#: resources/xnec2c.glade:11020
msgid ""
"Reinhard rational soft-compressor with knee k.\n"
"Adjust k in the animate dialog."
msgstr ""
"Reinhards rationella mjukkompressor med knä k.\n"
"Justera k i animeringsdialogen."

#: resources/xnec2c.glade:11021
msgid "_Reinhard"
msgstr "_Reinhard"

#: resources/xnec2c.glade:11032
msgid ""
"Hyperbolic tangent transfer with contrast steepness a.\n"
"Adjust a in the animate dialog."
msgstr ""
"Hyperbolisk tangentöverföring med kontrastbrantheten a.\n"
"Justera a i animeringsdialogen."

